What is libvirt?
    Libvirt = libvirtd, virsh, API library

    $ virsh list --all
'use libvirt' usually means manage virtual machine using tools such as 'virsh', 'virt-manager', or 'virt-install' 
not directly use 'xm' or 'qemu-kvm'

Support: LXC (Linux Container), OpenVZ, QEMU, UML (User-mode Linux), 
	 Xen, VMWare, ...
